jacdac.WindSpeedReg.MaxWindSpeed:
Constant m/s u16.16 (uint32_t). Maximum speed that can be measured by the sensor.

jacdac.WindSpeedReg.WindSpeed:
Read-only m/s u16.16 (uint32_t). The velocity of the wind.

```
